commit dfcc325f55d580eb630f3b236eadf99f6b7d6ad6
Author: Alan Coopersmith <alan.coopersmith@oracle.com>
Date:   Fri Mar 23 19:38:07 2012 -0700

    Add savage_pciids.h to src/Makefile.am to fix distcheck
    
