Date:   Mon Apr 18 22:04:00 2011 +0200

    savage: Fix logic in waitHSync
    
    Bit-masking the result of a boolean negation seems pointless,
    so I guess this is what was intended: Only look at bit 0 of the
    inStatus result.
    
